// Earth Sphere campaign map — Starsector-shape continuous 2D space.
//
// POIs are points in normalized 0–100 space that the StarmapPanel maps to
// any SVG viewBox. There are NO edges and NO sectors: travel is straight-
// line burns through continuous space, with fuel + supplies + duration
// scaling to the Euclidean distance between two POIs. Encounters trigger
// at POI arrival (always), and probabilistically along long burns based
// on regional faction control.
//
// Major POIs are hand-authored at canonical UC astrography positions
// (Sides 1–7, Luna, Luna II, Earth orbit, asteroid clusters). Minor POIs
// (procedural — derelicts, signal sources, salvage fields, mining
// outposts) are scattered against `WORLD_SEED` at module import time and
// share the same shape.
//
// Each POI carries:
//   - id, nameZh, type, factionControlPre/Post (Phase 7 flips)
//   - pos {x,y} in 0..100 normalized space
//   - region: a thematic region tag the encounter generator filters on
//   - sceneId? optional binding to a walkable scene; player docks and
//     walks in instead of seeing an abstract event
//   - services? list of dock services (refuel, repair, refit, hire, store)
//   - encounterPoolId? override the region's pool for this POI specifically
//
// Region pools are listed under `regions[]`. The active region for a
// given fleet position is the closest region centroid (Voronoi-style).
// Phase 7 will flip `factionControlPost` on contested POIs at the war
// trigger; encounter pools also re-activate per region at that point.

{
  // Region centroids + thematic encounter pools. The captain's current
  // region is decided by which region centroid is nearest — softly
  // partitions the continuous map into encounter zones without forcing
  // a hard border. Encounters listed here are weighted bags of template
  // ids referenced by data/encounters.json5.
  regions: [
    {
      id: 'lunarSphere',
      nameZh: '月球圈',
      centroid: { x: 60, y: 45 },
      difficultyBand: 'tutorial',
      encounterPool: [
        { templateId: 'routine_jump', weight: 5 },
        { templateId: 'patrol_stop_civilian', weight: 2 },
        { templateId: 'distress_signal_minor', weight: 1 },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: 'side12cluster',
      nameZh: 'Side 1/2 集群',
      centroid: { x: 60, y: 28 },
      difficultyBand: 'low',
      encounterPool: [
        { templateId: 'routine_jump', weight: 4 },
        { templateId: 'patrol_stop_civilian', weight: 2 },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: 'side3approach',
      nameZh: 'Side 3 接近线',
      centroid: { x: 80, y: 50 },
      difficultyBand: 'mid',
      encounterPool: [
        { templateId: 'routine_jump', weight: 2 },
        { templateId: 'pirate_patrol', weight: 2 },
        { templateId: 'patrol_stop_civilian', weight: 2 },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: 'side45graveyard',
      nameZh: 'Side 4/5 集群',
      centroid: { x: 45, y: 68 },
      difficultyBand: 'mid',
      encounterPool: [
        { templateId: 'routine_jump', weight: 3 },
        { templateId: 'derelict_signal', weight: 2 },
        { templateId: 'salvage_field', weight: 1 },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: 'shoalZone',
      nameZh: '浅滩区',
      centroid: { x: 35, y: 55 },
      difficultyBand: 'mid',
      encounterPool: [
        { templateId: 'pirate_patrol', weight: 4 },
        { templateId: 'debris_hazard', weight: 2 },
        { templateId: 'distress_signal_trap', weight: 2 },
        { templateId: 'salvage_field', weight: 1 },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: 'earthOrbit',
      nameZh: '地球低轨',
      centroid: { x: 50, y: 50 },
      difficultyBand: 'low',
      encounterPool: [
        { templateId: 'routine_jump', weight: 5 },
        { templateId: 'patrol_stop_civilian', weight: 3 },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: 'outerBelt',
      nameZh: '外环',
